---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import LegalFooter from '../../components/LegalFooter.astro';
---
<Layout title="taerijay+protocol">
	<Header />
	<main class="w-full min-h-screen px-6 md:px-12 py-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-6 font-noto">
		<div class="border-b border-[#5B0E1B] pb-4 flex justify-between items-center font-spartan"><h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#FF6B00] lowercase">taerijay+protocol</h1><span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 border border-[#FF6B00] text-[#FF6B00] font-black rounded-full">🌐 REGULATION</span></div>
		<div class="p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-[#FF6B00] flex flex-col gap-4">
			<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">🌐 Global Traveler Code & Security</h3>
			<p class="text-white border-l-2 border-[#FF6B00] pl-2">해외 입국객 필수 공항 세관 및 대중교통 탑승 안전 수칙 명시함.<br/><span class="text-slate-400 font-spartan text-xs block mt-0.5">Legal security frameworks initialization.</span></p>
			<div class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-[#5B0E1B]/20 pt-4 mt-2 font-spartan text-sm">
				<span class="text-slate-200" id="ad2">Incheon International Airport Terminal 1 & 2</span>
				<button class="copy-btn bg-[#5B0E1B]/40 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded border border-[#5B0E1B] text-xs font-bold" data-target="ad2">COPY</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
	<LegalFooter />
</Layout>